        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <salute>My dear M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>. Babbage</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I am very much obliged to you for sending me cards for your parties, but I am afraid of accepting them, for I should meet some people there, to whom I have sworn by all the saints in Heaven, I never go out, &amp; should, therefore, be ashamed to meet them.— I assure you I feel very grateful for your kindness to me.</p>
<p>Believe me | Most sincerely y<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi>. | Chas. Darwin</p>
<p>Wednesd Morning</p>
<p>36 Gr<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>. Marlbro’ St<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>.—</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        

        

